column100:
We are looking for full-time or part-time kitchen assistants for Restaurant Morsel Bao at Godthåbsvej 48, Frederiksberg with start-up as soon as possible! 
 We expect you 
 
 know and have worked in a professional kitchen for at least 6 months  
 motivated to work in the kitchen - with the tasks associated with both cleaning and washing dishes      
 can work independently and structured 
 are responsible and able to work in a fast-paced environment 
 
 We offer an exciting position with lots of challenges, and salaries that match your qualifications. Please send your CV to info@morselbao.dk 
 We are looking forward hearing from you!
